    "path": "src/agent/task",
    "name": "task",
    "purpose": "Owns the agent task runtime. step.rs defines the StepSequence ordering key, the Step record, and the StepKind/ToolStepKind/ModelStepKind/UserStepKind classification enums; task_context.rs defines TaskContext, the shared runtime data holding the task signature, a mutex-guarded model backend, client/host senders, the execution and step WorkQueues, and the shared tokio runtime that all Task worker threads block_on to emit events; task.rs defines Task, which owns an Arc<TaskContext>, an internal SessionEvent channel, and a worker handle, and drives model steps, streams task status to the client, and forwards host execution events over the shared runtime; execution.rs defines the Execution record. mod.rs is namespace and re-export wiring only.",
